                    <span class="diagonal-word"> your app on the App Store and Google Play</span><br>
                    <span class="diagonal-word">while keeping you involved every step of the way.</span>
                </p>

                <div class="diagonal-btn-wrapper">
                    <button class="diagonal-join-btn">Join for $9.99/m</button>
                    <button class="diagonal-readmore-btn">Read more</button>
                </div>
